@host = http://localhost:5062

### Generate standup (mid-week, current week)
POST {{host}}/api/standup/generate?weekOf=2026-04-06
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate standup (weekly summary)
POST {{host}}/api/standup/generate?weekOf=2026-04-06&commandType=weekly
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate standup (no items — expects 400)
POST {{host}}/api/standup/generate?weekOf=1999-01-04
Content-Type: application/json

### Generate standup (missing weekOf — expects 400)
POST {{host}}/api/standup/generate
Content-Type: application/json

### Get saved standup for today
GET {{host}}/api/standup?date=2026-04-07

### Save standup
POST {{host}}/api/standup
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "markdown": "### Did you complete your One Thing yesterday?\nCrushed it.",
  "date": "2026-04-07"
}

### Get saved standup (no entry — expects 404)
GET {{host}}/api/standup?date=1999-01-01
